# Employee Result and Performance Analyzer

A **JavaFX + HTML (WebView)** based desktop application to manage, analyze, and evaluate employee performance using KPI scores.
The project demonstrates **Java–JavaScript communication**, validation, and a modern UI inside a Java desktop app.

---

## Features

* Add, update, delete employee records
* KPI-based performance calculation (Communication, Work Quality, Technical)
* Automatic average and grade calculation
* Validation rules:

  * Employee ID must contain letters + numbers (e.g., `EMP101`)
  * KPI values must be numeric and ≤ 100
  * Duplicate employee IDs are not allowed
* Search employee by ID
* Sort employees by grade (A → B → C → F)
* Refresh and view all records
* Dialog-based success and error messages
* Auto-clear forms after successful operations
* Clean, centered, tab-based UI

---

